	<description><![CDATA[<b>Art Text Rotator</b> is a Joomla! text scroller module. © <a href="http://www.artetics.com">Artetics.com</a> - Where art meets aesthetics.<link href="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/library/uikit/css/uikit.almost-flat.min.css"rel="stylesheet"><script src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/library/uikit/js/uikit.min.js"></script><hr><div class="uk-grid"><div class="uk-width-medium-1-2"><div><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/art-text-rotator-logo-600-ls.jpg"style="max-width:40px"> <span style="font-size:24px;position:relative;top:5px">Art Text Rotator</span></div></div></div><hr><p>Art Text Rotator is a free module. Artetics.com provides limited support for free products. However we do provide some resources to make seeking help with free products easy. 'Discussions' below is our support forum. 'Knowledgebase' is our documentation. 'Premium Support' is for purchasing support time for feature requests or custom modifications. 'Contact Us' is to send our team an email.<p>We hope you enjoy Art Text Rotator!<div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box uk-margin"><div class="uk-grid uk-width-1-1"data-uk-grid-margin=""><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4 uk-row-first"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_easydiscuss&view=index&Itemid=902&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target="_blank">Discussions</a></div><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/support/knowledgebase?utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target="_blank">Knowledgebase</a></div><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&view=product&layout=show&Itemid=903&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target="_blank">Premium Support</a></div><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/contact-us?utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target="_blank">Contact Us</a></div></div></div><h2>Popular Artetics.com Extensions</h2><div class="uk-grid uk-grid-width-large-1-2 uk-grid-width-medium-1-2 uk-grid-width-small-1-1 uk-margin-large"data-uk-grid-margin><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-fast-youtube-logo-600.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Fast Youtube</h3><p>Reduce YouTube video load time by up to 40% over the standard embed code and make your YouTube videos responsive at the same time!<div><a href="https://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=79&name=art-fast-youtube&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a> <a href="https://www.artetics.com/demo/art-fast-youtube?utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button"target="_blank">Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-calendar-logo-600-ls.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Calendar</h3><p>Art Calendar is used to create visually rich, interactive, modern calendars that can be quickly deployed using Google Calendar API.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-calendar&cid=1&Itemid=469&category_pathway=19&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_artcalendar&view=artcalendar&id=1&Itemid=106&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button"target="_blank">Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-timeline-logo-600-ls.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Timeline</h3><p>Art Timeline enables anyone to build visually rich, timelines. Load events from Admin, Google Drive, Google Calendar or SQL Query.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-timeline&cid=2&Itemid=469&category_pathway=19&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=27&Itemid=130&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button"target="_blank">Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-data-logo-600-ls.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Data</h3><p>Art Data makes it easy to create 2 types of tables and 12 types of chart and use templates to control the style of your tables and charts.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=7&name=art-data&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/art-data?utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button"target="_blank">Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-table-logo-600-ls.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Table</h3><p>Art Table is used to insert sortable, searchable tables, multiple types of data charts for easy data presentation from multiple data sources.<div><a href="http://artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-table&cid=23&Itemid=469&category_pathway=19&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=26&Itemid=129&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button"target="_blank">Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-sexy-lightbox-logo-600-ls.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Sexy Lightbox</h3><p>Art Sexy Lightbox is used for displaying photos, galleries, Imgur, Picasa, Google Photos, Flickr, Photobucket, VirtueMart and more.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=8&name=art-sexy-lightbox&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=21&Itemid=124&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button"target="_blank">Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-feature-tour-logo-600.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Feature Tour</h3><p>Art Feature Tour is a step by step guide and site introduction tool for Joomla to give a 'tour' of areas of importance to your site.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=78&name=art-feature-tour&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/art-feature-tour-illumination?utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button"target="_blank">Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class="uk-clearfix"><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class="uk-margin-right"src="../modules/mod_arttextrotator/images/popular/art-adminer-logo-600-ls.jpg"style="max-width:140px"></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Adminer</h3><p>Art Adminer is a smart and lightweight database management component and can be used to read, write, alter and many more tasks.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-adminer&cid=58&Itemid=469&category_pathway=24&utm_source=Art_Text_Rotator_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTextRotator_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target="_blank">Learn More</a></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></description>
